msgid ""
"For surface terms — Neumann tractions, Robin BCs, penalty contact — "
":class:`~tensormesh.FacetAssembler` runs the same dispatch over *facet* "
"quadrature instead of volume quadrature. The signature contract is "
"identical to :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`'s except that the basis "
