"(interior entries are zero). Summing all entries recovers the perimeter "
"exactly. ``FacetAssembler`` defaults to integrating over "
"``mesh.boundary_mask``; pass ``boundary_mask=...`` to ``from_mesh`` to "
"restrict to a labelled sub-boundary."
